These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure
1. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure    | scientific   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, scooter
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Transport   | scooter | roller        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: carrot, cherry
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Food   | cherry    | carrot |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the indonesian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Nationality       | chinese | indonesian    |

