.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, mystery
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, folk
1. the fan of folk is the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the fan of country is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Movie-Genre          | mystery | western |
| Music-Genre   | folk | country   |

